name: Birder
0:
”Alexa, open Birder Assistant”
”Post Hello from my Echo”
”What are global trends?”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: birder assistant
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Birder is the first Alexa Skill which allows you to manage your Twitter account using Alexa. You can post new tweets and browse global trends.
Birder is NOT affiliated with Twitter in any way!
